  "readme_html": "\n        \n          <p>Huihui 3.5:67B is a merged model created by combining <a href=\"https://huggingface.co/Qwen/Qwen3.5-35B-A3B\" rel=\"nofollow\">Qwen/Qwen3.5-35B-A3B</a> and <a href=\"https://huggingface.co/Hcompany/Holo3-35B-A3B\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hcompany/Holo3-35B-A3B</a>.  The base model is <a href=\"https://huggingface.co/Qwen/Qwen3.5-35B-A3B\" rel=\"nofollow\">Qwen/Qwen3.5-35B-A3B</a>, and the total number of experts has been expanded from 256 to 512 experts, while still activating only 8 experts per token.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Note</strong> Huihui 3.5:67B is not an ablated model.</p>\n\n<p>Welcome everyone to test it. If you require the unquantized model, please send an email to support@huihui.ai.</p>\n\n<h3>References</h3>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/Qwen/Qwen3.5-35B-A3B\" rel=\"nofollow\">Qwen/Qwen3.5-35B-A3B</a>\n<a href=\"https://huggingface.co/Hcompany/Holo3-35B-A3B\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hcompany/Holo3-35B-A3B</a></p>\n\n        \n      "
